Oyesade "Sade" Olatoye (amụrụ na ụbọchị iri abụọ na ise n'ọnwa Jenụwarị afọ 1997) bụ nwa afọ Naijiria na-eme egwuregwu na-asọ mpi na shot put na ịtụba hama
Ọ gbanwere nkwado site na United States n'afọ 2019
Ọ nọchitere anya Naijiria na shot put nke 2019 World Championships na Doha n'erughị nke ikpeazụ
Na mbido afọ ahụ, o ritere ihe nrite abụọ na 2019 African Games.
Àtụ:African Games champions in women's shot putÀtụ:Footer African Champions women's hammer throw
